headline: REV Group (NYSE:REVG) Q4 Earnings: Leading The Heavy Transportation Equipment Pack
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how REV Group (NYSE:REVG) and the rest of the heavy transportation equipment stocks fared in Q4.
